\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 中的二阶微分算符可以分解为两个一阶微分算符的
\color blue
乘积
\color inherit
：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}-a^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial x^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}-a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)
\]

\end_inset

引入坐标变换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\xi\\
\eta
\end{bmatrix}\coloneqq\begin{bmatrix}x+at\\
x-at
\end{bmatrix}\implies\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\xi & \partial_{t}\eta\\
\partial_{x}\xi & \partial_{x}\eta
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}a & -a\\
1 & 1
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

只要该变换是非退化的，即 
\begin_inset Formula $a\ne0$
\end_inset

，就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}-a\partial_{x}\\
\partial_{t}+a\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & -a\\
1 & +a
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix} & -2a\\
2a
